	(text "Chaos Modulation DAC Outputs:\nG25/DAC -> GPS_TUNE (VCO1)\nG26/DAC -> WIFI_TUNE (VCO2)\n\nAnalog Inputs:\nG36/ADC <- THERM_ADC (temperature sense, ADC1_CH0)\nG0/ADC  <- BATT_ADC (battery voltage, via divider)\n\nDigital Control:\nG33 -> BIAS_EN (charge pump enable)\nG32 -> RELAY_CTRL (WiFi PA switch)"
